Tests use Bun test. When mocking, either use the bulit-in Bun testing imports or use `import { jest } from 'bun:test'` for Jest-compatible mocking.

## Module Mocks

When mocking a module, always use Bun's test library with this pattern instead of using jest mock:

```
import { test } from 'bun:test';

await mock.module('path/to/module', {
  return {
    // mocked module
  }
});
```
